  "base_path": "/book-pupil-theory-test",
  "content_id": "9d81d175-80c8-4ed3-a611-48765cce8a77",
  "description": "Book theory tests for your pupils, check or change appointment details, or cancel tests.",
  "details": {
    "department_analytics_profile": "",
    "external_related_links": [

    ],
    "introductory_paragraph": "<p>If you’re an instructor or trainer, use this service to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>book theory tests</li>\n  <li>confirm your pupil’s details before the test</li>\n  <li>check appointments</li>\n  <li>change or cancel appointments</li>\n</ul>\n\n<div role=\"note\" aria-label=\"Information\" class=\"application-notice info-notice\">\n<p>There’s a different service to <a href=\"/book-theory-test\">book your own theory test</a>.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"register-to-book-theory-tests\">Register to book theory tests</h2>\n<p>You must be <a href=\"/register-book-driving-tests-for-pupils\">registered to book tests</a>. You’ll get your Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) business ID, username and password when you register to book.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"book-and-manage-theory-tests-online\">Book and manage theory tests online</h2>\n<p>You’ll need your:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency (DVSA) business ID</li>\n  <li>username</li>\n  <li>password</li>\n  <li>credit or debit card</li>\n  <li>pupil’s driving licence number if you’re confirming their details</li>\n</ul>\n",
    "more_information": "\n<p>You can book the following types of test:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>car</li>\n  <li>motorcycle</li>\n  <li>lorry and bus, including the Driver Certificate of Professional Competence (CPC) part 1 (theory) and part 2 (case studies) tests</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"book-without-a-pupils-details\">Book without a pupil’s details</h2>\n\n<p>You can book tests up to 3 months in advance. You do not have to give a pupil’s details when you book. This is known as being a ‘trainer booker’.</p>\n\n<p>You must confirm the pupil’s details by 4pm at least one clear working day before the test. Working days do not include Sundays and public holidays.</p>\n\n<div class=\"example\">\n<h3 id=\"example\">Example</h3>\n<p>Confirm the pupil’s details by 4pm on Wednesday if the test is on Friday.</p>\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"change-or-cancel-a-test\">Change or cancel a test</h2>\n\n<p>You must give at least 3 full working days’ notice to change or cancel the test, or you’ll have to pay again. Monday to Saturday count as working days but Sundays and public holidays do not.</p>\n\n<p>Find out when you can get a refund if you <a href=\"/change-theory-test\">change a theory test</a> or <a href=\"/cancel-theory-test\">cancel a theory test</a> at short notice.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"help-with-your-bookings\">Help with your bookings</h2>\n\n<p>Contact <abbr title=\"Driver and Vehicle Standards Agency\">DVSA</abbr> to get help booking theory tests for your pupils.</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p>DVSA theory test booking support<br>\n<a href=\"mailto:theorycustomerservices@dvsa.gov.uk\">theorycustomerservices@dvsa.gov.uk</a><br>\nTelephone: 0300 200 1122 (then press the 2-digit <a href=\"/guidance/use-the-dvsa-fast-track-service-for-driver-and-rider-trainers\">fast track code</a>)<br>\nMonday to Friday, 8am to 4pm<br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n",
    "start_button_text": "Start now",
    "transaction_start_link": "https://www.trainer.book-theory-test.service.gov.uk/",
